name: Air Fryer French Toast Sticks
author: Yoly
summary: Crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, these French toast sticks make a delicious breakfast!
ingredients: 4 slices day-old bread, cut into thirds
1 teaspoon confectioners' sugar, or to taste
directions: Mix eggs, milk, butter, vanilla extract, and cinnamon together in a bowl
Line an air fryer basket with parchment paper
Dip each piece of bread into the milk mixture and place in the basket
Make sure they are not touching; cook in batches if necessary
Preheat the air fryer to 370 degrees F (188 degrees C)
Add basket and cook bread for 6 minutes; flip and cook for 3 minutes more
Sprinkle each stick with confectioners' sugar
